    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chairs designed to be used in dentists' offices that allow the patient to be positioned in various ways for dental work. These are usually accessorized with various appliances. Modern dental chairs are equipped with pneumatics for raising or lowering the chair itself.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
